     <div type="argument">
   <pb facs="5"/>
   <head>The Argument.</head>
   <l>VErtue is Wisedomes light, Wisedome her loue,</l>
   <l>And Constancie her only lifes delight:</l>
   <l>Which Patience in Humility doth proue,</l>
   <l>Humility the eye of Vertues sight:</l>
   <l>I hat sees the Graces branches of the Tree,</l>
   <l>Which figures God, in whom their Glories be.</l>
</div>
